node.text:
You know Barbie, but have you met… Barbie? 💖 That’s right; Barbie Roberts meets Barbie Roberts, and they have more in common than just their name! The two became fast friends and chose nicknames inspired by their hometowns – Malibu and Brooklyn – to better differentiate when they’re together.
 
Gather your kids and join the two friends in this dorm room unboxing to get to know #Barbie “Brooklyn” Roberts!

node.text: For three years, the Barbie Día de Muertos series has paid tribute to the Mexican festival of remembrance and its customs, symbols and rituals. Now for the first time ever, Barbie introduces a collectible Ken doll to the series. Wearing a charro-inspired look featuring a sarape and embroidered shirt, with face painted in a striking calavera design, this doll is the perfect gift for all who celebrate.

node.text: When we celebrate those we’ve lost, their memories live on in us forever. Now in its third year, the Barbie Día De Muertos series continues to honor the rich culture and symbolism of the Mexican festival of remembrance, and for the first time ever is joined by a collectible Ken doll to be treasured as a new addition to your family traditions.

node.text: Every fall, many families with roots in Mexico honor their loved ones by celebrating Día de Muertos and commemorating those they’ve lost. Now in its third year of the series, the 2021 Día De Muertos Barbie doll continues to pay tribute to the holiday in a traditional embroidered dress, a crown of marigolds, and symbolic calavera face painting, making this the perfect collectible gift for all who celebrate.

node.text: Have you met Rafa (and Gato 🐕) yet? Watch and rewatch #BarbieBigCityBigDreams this weekend to get to know Barbie and Barbie’s newest friend and fashion designer!

node.accessibility_caption: Barbie Brooklyn performs on stage

node.text: Hit the stage with Barbie “Brooklyn” Roberts and play out all of your music dreams! From an iconic sparkly guitar to a matching light-up dress, Brooklyn puts the ⭐️ in popstar!

node.accessibility_caption: Barbie Brooklyn performs on stage
Barbie Brooklyn sings into the micriphone
A closeup of Barbie Brooklyn’s guitar
Barbie Brooklyn and Barbie Malibu stand together on stage

node.text: Big dreams can come true! Especially when you have your best friend at your side 💖💜 Sing along with Barbie and Barbie and experience the magic of music and friendship!

node.accessibility_caption: Barbie Malibu plays her guitar and performs on stage

node.text: Malibu in New York! With a perfect performance outfit and all of the popstar accessories, Barbie “Malibu” Roberts is (one of 😉) New York’s latest icons!
